title.en: MySQL, import SQL file from console

description.en: Importing SQL data in MySQL is very simple through PHPMyAdmin, either from the import option or directly executing the SQL. The thing gets complicated when there are a lot of data and the SQL file weighs more than the one allowed by the import option or, in the SQL web executer, it becomes heavy to make a simple cut and paste (ctr + cy ctrl + v) due to the large amount of information.
